title: [Q&A] Why We're NOT Global Warming Activists (And Why I Choose, Instead…)
description:
A lot of autobiographical material ensues in discussing what I do and don't try to research, record videos on and change —as an author or activist.  But, in two words, the answer is: "The Establishment".
Support the channel on Patreon (for $1 per month) and your questions, also, can result in video replies of this kind:
https://www.patreon.com/a_bas_le_ciel/
